lass=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講真，就算政府唔支持魚業，但班後生唔入行，點都係會式微"},{"pid":"eb77378f674fc9b06280df21fa15dd90186d642f","tid":276620,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:50:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鬼國並非浪得虛明</blockquote><br />\n真正破壞全球生態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55789df268357b8b02e77b39df97c5e5ccb5cfd","tid":276620,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:51:29.000Z","msg":"支那人根本無當支那係自己屋企<br />\n整爛左咩？未去英美澳加囉，最重要係我發達"},{"pid":"00dfd9c89be68748181afff85cec48886281ce24","tid":276620,"uid":41470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T02:54:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那人根本無當支那係自己屋企<br />\n整爛左咩？未去英美澳加囉，最重要係我發達</blockquote><br />\n好難明白點解會有人整爛自己屋企，又係自己屋企整埋啲爛傢私(豆腐渣工程)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"219f89e837ee5a9c34f10ff558d7971678419f06","tid":276620,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:05:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支那人根本無當支那係自己屋企<br />\n整爛左咩？未去英美澳加囉，最重要係我發達</blockquote><br />\n好難明白點解會有人整爛自己屋企，又係自己屋企整埋啲爛傢私(豆腐渣工程)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當自己係外人就唔難理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a5877de8f2a033dbe85364487224309788e485d","tid":276620,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:57:09.000Z","msg":"隨左泡菜會開槍唔信其他國家會跟<br />\n<br />\n成日搞既野都一齊攬炒"},{"pid":"5ea47fe1f22caf4c15512d1101701843ec970ef0","tid":276620,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T04:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea80ee8ffe7bcd731c5ae493ad403added67b7e","tid":276620,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:07:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>隨左泡菜會開槍唔信其他國家會跟<br />\n<br />\n成日搞既野都一齊攬炒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個個都炸你支那啦, 你以為人地怕支那國有牙咩？<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20160319/54885229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20160319%2F54885229&d=Qt0MqXQlWJQZma1h94VKXW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=c720a850\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20160319%2F54885229&h=3487859f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20160319/54885229</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">多國曾開火炸沉中國漁船</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20160319/large/1458363976_2673.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20160319%2Flarge%2F1458363976_2673.jpg&h=668cc789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印尼炸毀非法捕魚的外國漁船。<br />\n<br />\n中國漁業身陷海漁業資源日益枯竭，不得不到海外「開疆拓土」。中國農業部漁業漁政管理局副局長崔利鋒說：「我國漁業在世界上佔有重要地位，已成為全球海洋漁業第一大國。」中國遠洋漁業作業海域，已擴展到40個國家和地區的專屬經濟區，以及太平洋、印度洋、大西洋公海和南極海域，同時也惹怒全球，多國曾向中國漁船開火還擊。<br />\n<br />\n2016年3月14日<br />\n中國一艘遠洋漁船「魯煙遠漁010號」，被指在阿根廷海域非法捕魚，並且企圖撞向追捕的巡邏船。阿根廷海岸防衞隊稱鳴槍示警無效後，開火擊沉漁船，船員獲救，船長等4人被捕候審。中國大使向阿根廷政府提緊急交涉，外交部要求阿方立即徹查事件，並採取措施防止類似事件再發生。<br />\n<br />\n2015年12月8日<br />\n南韓海軍向越過半島西部海域「北方界限線」的中國漁政船，進行示警射擊，並「將其逼退」。<br />\n<br />\n2015年5月20日<br />\n印尼在數個港口同時炸毀41艘、據稱在印尼海域非法捕魚的外國漁船，其中有5艘來自越南、2艘來自泰國、11艘來自菲律賓以及1艘來自中國。<br />\n<br />\n2012年7月15-16日<br />\n兩艘來自中國山東的漁船，在日本海俄屬經濟區被扣留。一艘漁船有19名漁民，另外1艘有17名漁民。事發當日，中國漁船對俄方詢問不作回答，並試圖逃逸，當俄邊防人員試圖登船時，該船企圖抗拒，俄邊防軍被迫向該船開火。<br />\n綜合報道"},{"pid":"0b39b626c62d030862fa7d168059467d00828827","tid":276620,"uid":8009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T05:31:41.000Z","msg":"Sor<br />\n抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1682e99972919dd71c0ef7a69d7732efeef949b","tid":276620,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>支那人根本無當支那係自己屋企<br />\n整爛左咩？未去英美澳加囉，最重要係我發達</blockquote><br />\n好難明白點解會有人整爛自己屋企，又係自己屋企整埋啲爛傢私(豆腐渣工程)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當自己係外人就唔難理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地諗住搵夠錢, 就移民去外國, 所以唔會理自己國家變成點"},{"pid":"40522ef43b4bee1cff3d1b25cefe1742c38f3325","tid":276620,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:41:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>支那人根本無當支那係自己屋企<br />\n整爛左咩？未去英美澳加囉，最重要係我發達</blockquote><br />\n好難明白點解會有人整爛自己屋企，又係自己屋企整埋啲爛傢私(豆腐渣工程)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當自己係外人就唔難理解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地諗住搵夠錢, 就移民去外國, 所以唔會理自己國家變成點</blockquote><br />\n中國人最變態係<br />\n<br />\n整D 毒奶粉, 毒疫苗 出來害下一代"},{"pid":"946dc85999217bd91315bfc4a518ea115d164c04","tid":276620,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>隨左泡菜會開槍唔信其他國家會跟<br />\n<br />\n成日搞既野都一齊攬炒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n